    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, this beauty is something special. It\u2019s been pampered like a member of the family\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed with love. It honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There might be a tiny, tiny mark here or there if you use a magnifying glass, but to anyone else, it\u2019s practically perfect. It drives like a dream and turns heads at every stoplight. I\u2019m looking for a fellow car lover who will cherish it as much as I have. Come by and see it for yourself; I promise you\u2019ll fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 48500.0,
