      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a time capsule wrapped in hand-polished steel and sculpted by the winds of a more elegant era. Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide through winding coastal roads, the engine humming a low, confident melody that echoes like a symphony through the valley. Every curve of its body tells a story of unyielding grace, finished in a luster that captures the world in its reflection. The interior greets you with the rich, unmistakable scent of premium leather and the tactile satisfaction of chrome that catches the light like a rare jewel. To drive this is to command a masterpiece; to own it is to inherit a legacy of pure, unadulterated automotive passion. This is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for.",
      "price": 48500.0,
